# Copy to .env and fill in. Used by server/index.js.
# Also merged: repo root `.env` is loaded after this file (missing vars only), so you can keep YOUTUBE_* next to Vite in the root `.env`.
# Start API: cd server && node index.js (default PORT=4000). From repo root, npm run dev (or npm run preview)
# proxies /api to http://127.0.0.1:4000 so Crystal + globe API calls work without VITE_API_URL.
#
# --- YouTube Data API (globe country search + Crystal Ball video search) ---
# Google Cloud → enable YouTube Data API v3 → create API key(s).
# Quota: default ~10,000 units/day; each search.list costs 100 units. If you see quotaExceeded,
# wait until daily reset (Pacific), add more keys from other GCP projects (YOUTUBE_API_KEY_2, _3),
# or request a higher quota (APIs & Services → YouTube Data API v3 → Quotas).
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY_2=   # optional — tried automatically when an earlier key hits quota or auth errors
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY_3=   # optional — third fallback in the same order
#
# How long to reuse country results before calling YouTube again (ms). Default 86400000 = 24h.
# GLOBE_COUNTRY_CACHE_MS=86400000
#
# --- YouTube playlists (OAuth — playlists are created on YOUR Google account) ---
# 1. Google Cloud → APIs & Services → Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Desktop or Web).
# 2. Add redirect: http://127.0.0.1:8890/oauth2callback
# 3. Put client id/secret below, then: cd server && node youtube-auth.js
# 4. Paste the printed refresh token:
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
YOUTUBE_OAUTH_REFRESH_TOKEN=
#
# Troubleshooting: Error 403 access_denied on Google’s consent page → APIs & Services →
# OAuth consent screen → under “Test users”, add the Gmail you sign in with (required while Publishing status is “Testing”).
# “Internal” user type only allows Workspace accounts, not personal Gmail.
#
# --- Spotify (optional — Luffa “mood” matching + legacy /api/crystal-youtube-to-spotify) ---
# Not required for globe or YouTube playlists.
# SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
# SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
# SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=
# CRYSTAL_SPOTIFY_LOOKUP_MS=22000
# SPOTIFY_COUNTRY_GAP_MS=1200
#
# Luffa bot: LUFFA_BOT_SECRET (Robot Key). Optional: CLAUDE_API_KEY for AI intents/replies.
# LUFFA_DEBUG=1
# LUFFA_POLL_MS=700
# SHOWCASE-BATTLE poll length (ms). Default 20000 = 20s. Min 5000.
# LUFFA_BATTLE_SHOWCASE_MS=20000
# CLAUDE_API_KEY=
# LUFFA_BROADCAST_GROUP_UID=
# Showcase: SHOWCASE-DIGEST | SHOWCASE-ALERT | SHOWCASE-BATTLE | SHOWCASE-PLAYLIST | SHOWCASE-MOOD
#
# Crystal / globe archives: ../archive/*.json (gitignored)

LUFFA_BOT_SECRET=
